s-center\"><div class=\"animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-muted via-muted/50 to-muted bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-lg h-3 w-24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-muted via-muted/50 to-muted bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-lg h-4 w-20 hidden sm:block\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-muted via-muted/50 to-muted bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-lg h-3 w-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-muted via-muted/50 to-muted bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-lg h-3 w-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"animate-shimmer bg-gradient-to-r from-muted via-muted/50 to-muted bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-lg h-4 w-14 hidden sm:block\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mt-4 text-[10px] text-muted-foreground/60\">Data sourced from: UNDP Nigeria 2024 · UNFPA Nigeria HumanitarianSitRep 2025 · UNHCR Protection Sector 2024 · Nigeria HRP 2025</p></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 border-b border-border bg-secondary/20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"mb-8 sm:mb-12 md:mb-16 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold\">Platform Features</h2><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl\">Comprehensive tools designed for researchers, policymakers, and humanitarian organizations.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-8\" style=\"transition-duration:500ms\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/10 hover:border-accent/50 cursor-pointer card-glow bg-card border-border h-full active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform\"><div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 rounded flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner\" style=\"background-color:#f4b94233\"><div class=\"h-5 w-5 sm:h-6 sm:w-6 rounded shadow-lg\" style=\"background-color:#f4b942;box-shadow:0 4px 12px -2px #f4b94280\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-base sm:text-lg\">State &amp; LGA Insights</h3><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-muted-foreground\">Deep-dive into BAY state-specific and LGA-level data with humanitarian and youth metrics.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-8\" style=\"transition-duration:500ms\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/10 hover:border-accent/50 cursor-pointer card-glow bg-card border-border h-full active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform\"><div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 rounded flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner\" style=\"background-color:#f4b94233\"><div class=\"h-5 w-5 sm:h-6 sm:w-6 rounded shadow-lg\" style=\"background-color:#f4b942;box-shadow:0 4px 12px -2px #f4b94280\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-base sm:text-lg\">Comparative Analysis</h3><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-muted-foreground\">Compare metrics across Borno, Adamawa, and Yobe to identify regional patterns.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-8\" style=\"transition-duration:500ms\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/10 hover:border-accent/50 cursor-pointer card-glow bg-card border-border h-full active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform\"><div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 rounded flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner\" style=\"background-color:#f4b94233\"><div class=\"h-5 w-5 sm:h-6 sm:w-6 rounded shadow-lg\" style=\"background-color:#f4b942;box-shadow:0 4px 12px -2px #f4b94280\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-base sm:text-lg\">AI-Powered Trends</h3><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-muted-foreground\">Machine learning discovers crisis patterns and predictive trends specific to the BAY region.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-8\" style=\"transition-duration:500ms\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/10 hover:border-accent/50 cursor-pointer card-glow bg-card border-border h-full active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform\"><div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12 rounded flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner\" style=\"background-color:#f4b94233\"><div class=\"h-5 w-5 sm:h-6 sm:w-6 rounded shadow-lg\" style=\"background-color:#f4b942;box-shadow:0 4px 12px -2px #f4b94280\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-base sm:text-lg\">Policy Briefs</h3><p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base text-muted-foreground\">Generate policy recommendations backed by BAY-focused real-time data and analysis.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 border-b border-border bg-gradient-to-b from-background to-secondary/20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-8\" style=\"transition-duration:500ms\"><div class=\"mb-8 sm:mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center space-y-3 sm:space-y-4\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-2 py-0.5 font-medium whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:rin